description:
Cutthroat Kitchen - Season 1, Episode 3





Tac'o the Town

n this episode full of culinary curveballs, we'll see if one chef can tempt the judge when they're forced to make tacos with bologna. Then we'll find out who the real traitors are as the chefs try to derail each other's Eggs Benedict. And finally we'll see if one chef can hold it together while they try to keep their crab cake from falling apart.




Original Air Date: 25-Aug-2013
